主要翻译
 
blurt [sth] # vtr (say on impulse)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 冲口而出 chōng kǒu ér chū TC Traditional Chinese 衝口而出  
 -- "It wasn't me!" Jack blurted defensively.
 -- “不是我！”杰克脱口而出，保持着戒备。

动词短语 
 
blurt [sth] out vtr phrasal sep (say on impulse)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 脱口说出  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 冲口而出 chōng kǒu ér chū TC Traditional Chinese 衝口而出 
 -- To his mother's horror, he blurted out all the details of her illness.
 -- 他忽然冲口说出了自己母亲病情的所有细节，让母亲非常惊恐。

在这些条目还发现' blurt '：
在英文解释里：
blunder

标题中含有单词 'blurt' 的论坛讨论：



an unclerical blurt of Anglo-Saxon derivation

